title: Swig Says Business is Best Done in the Office
itunes:title: Swig Says Business is Best Done in the Office
description:
Kent Swig, President of Swig Equities, discusses the state of New York City real estate and return to the office as we come out of the pandemic. Hosts: Carol Massar and Mike Regan. Producer: Paul Brennan.
